Package frc.robot.BreakerLib.util

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BreakerArbitraryFeedforwardProvider
    A class that acts as a provider for arbitrary feedforward demand values used with the Talon or SparkMax motor controller's integrated PID.
    BreakerBitField
    A class that represents a modifiable bit field for user convienance
    BreakerJSONUtil
    A convienent class with wrappers around the jackson JSON reader library's functions for easy access
    BreakerLibVersion
    A class representing the current version of the BreakerLib library you are useing, format is yy.major.minor (EX: "V22.8.1" -> 2022, major version 8, minor version 1)
    BreakerRoboRIO
    RoboRIO wrapper class utilizing Subsystem framework.
    BreakerTriplet<L,​M,​R>
    A 3-argument companion to the Pair class provided by WPILib
